enum MXCAM_STAT_ERR

Error and status codes of libmxcam.

Most of libmxcam functions return 0 on success.a negative value indicates its a libusb error.other wise one of the these codes on failure

Enumerator:
MXCAM_OK 

Success (no error).

MXCAM_STAT_EEPROM_FW_UPGRADE_START 

Started EEPROM FW Upgrade.

MXCAM_STAT_EEPROM_FW_UPGRADE_COMPLETE 

Completed EEPROM FW Upgrade.

MXCAM_STAT_SNOR_FW_UPGRADE_START 

Started SNOR FW Upgrade.

MXCAM_STAT_SNOR_FW_UPGRADE_COMPLETE 

Completed SNOR FW Upgrade.

MXCAM_STAT_FW_UPGRADE_COMPLETE 

Completed FW Upgrade.

MXCAM_STAT_EEPROM_ERASE_IN_PROG 

EEPROM Erase in progress.

MXCAM_STAT_EEPROM_SAVE_IN_PROG 

EEPROM config save in progress.

MXCAM_ERR_FW_SNOR_FAILED 

SNOR FW upgrade failed.

Unsupported Flash memory.

MXCAM_ERR_TCW_FLASH_WRITE
